{"tid":979801,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"昨晚又夢見你 你最近如何","createTime":"2019-01-13T04:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T05:24:27.000Z","uid":201671,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"75b639130a209f71901631d9e50996780ab50f76","tid":979801,"uid":201671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"一齊五年幾六年<br />\n你選擇一個識咗年幾嘅男人<br />\n因為新男友一句<br />\nDum曬我送嘅所有禮物同相<br />\nBlock埋我ig fb<br />\n話佢唔想我地再有任何聯絡<br />\n<br />\n早排喺街撞見你 只係互相微微一笑<br />\n明明好多嘢想講 嗰刻個腦一片空白<br />\n<br />\n五年幾感情 承諾一生 一齊計劃將來<br />\n結果變成過路人 一句野都講唔岀口<br />\n<br />\n分開咗兩年都會不時諗起你<br />\n但你應該一早唔記得咗我<br />\n唉 好l sad <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18c915288c3781a40b115b2e1d73af0f753a7b1","tid":979801,"uid":201671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"最on9係佢同新男友幾個月就散咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b5a218182c3f03a103d1f2f93b992b8510d469","tid":979801,"uid":201671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:20:02.000Z","msg":"春叫完就比心機返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15aee160b9001234a107692c2542c61d9c69d7b3","tid":979801,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"佢飛你？出軌？"},{"pid":"3994d31e5f412ef1935e2478d9fa9449683fb1bf","tid":979801,"uid":227691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e18c915288c3781a40b115b2e1d73af0f753a7b1","tid":979801,"uid":201671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"最on9係佢同新男友幾個月就散咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T04:30:16.000Z","msg":"咁佢有冇搵返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />